{"tid":2348023,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"( 連登有愛 ）我想搵返個故仔！","createTime":"2020-12-31T12:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T12:20:52.000Z","uid":312882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ea02f1f13df6cbe429aed2601b72019d3436a2c8","tid":2348023,"uid":312882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:19:20.000Z","msg":"個內容是咁的<br />\n唔記得個男主角係地獄使者定咩<br />\n只要幫3個死者投胎轉世 佢就完成自己嘅任務 就可以投胎轉世 <br />\n第一個死者好似係肥仔嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話想做有錢人同靚仔 但係佢嘅代價係有心臟病<br />\n<br />\n第二個死者係女歌手<br />\n好似因為生前做咗人第三者 被人網絡欺凌所以自殺( 唔記得咗係咪咁 ) 話想做被人愛戴嘅人  不過佢嘅代價係 愛佢嘅人要付出自己生命<br />\n<br />\n第三個好似係一個平凡嘅女仔<br />\n話唔知點解自己係度 總之就係一個平凡嘅女主角<br />\n<br />\n大概好似墨說個啲故咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係個作者好似唔係佢<br />\n希望各位巴打同絲打可以幫到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝大家有個開心嘅除夕夜 冇另一半嘅可以圍爐取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />THX"},{"pid":"36d3207bbfd5c51debadf260c0a8f8a1f0bc9696","tid":2348023,"uid":312882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:24:13.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"401be00ff79aaf2cc180e4450082629a594041a5","tid":2348023,"uid":312882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:00:18.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"c39cdd1b59e0a16972f376982caf2e5998a217e4","tid":2348023,"uid":312882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:03:32.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"8a654c752b411cd97c42eab23e73de577ac68c56","tid":2348023,"uid":312882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T14:57:25.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"5420920dbe6f419dc6c7a32e98dde578cd0d75dd","tid":2348023,"uid":312882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T14:57:36.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"0b7015adc0a140072f674eedb13a408075a14a4f","tid":2348023,"uid":312882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T14:58:51